Go into combat
Your move or enemy move
if your move choose
    1. Use a weapon
        pick between 3 weapons
    2. Use an item
        pick between items currently held
    3. Attempt to flee
        chance to succeed based on speed
    4. Inventory
        checks inventory
    5. Stats
        checks stat
    6. Enemy Stats
        checks enemy stat
if enemy move it will fight wtih magic or melee
    depends on which stat is higher but if close enough it will swap between the two
    may change to enemies having different attacks
repeat if enemy isnt dead

Player>Enemy>Player>Enemy
Player or Enemy based on speed
Player or Enemy 50/50 chance
